query:
UPDATE Solve
                SET solver_id = $1, solve_date = $2,
                    puzzle_id = $3, variant_id = $4, program_id = $5,
                    average = $6, blind = $7, filters = $8, macros = $9, one_handed = $10, computer_assisted = $11,
                    move_count = $12, speed_cs = $13, memo_cs = $14,
                    video_url = $15,
                    solver_notes = $16
                WHERE Solve.id = $17
